{"tid":2362572,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"港澳辦嚴厲強烈譴責英美澳加外長聲明","createTime":"2021-01-11T13:55:16.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-11T14:18:17.000Z","uid":230530,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"2d5d8991c4de17739eb26498b5e063f68070a718","tid":2362572,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T13:55:16.000Z","msg":"嬲"},{"pid":"178a07cdef8810e51603fca58b418507c181669b","tid":2362572,"uid":230530,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T13:55:41.000Z","msg":"國務院港澳辦強烈譴責美國國務卿和英國、澳洲、加拿大等國外長聯合發表涉港聲明，肆意詆毀《香港國安法》，粗暴干涉香港警方對戴耀廷等人涉嫌違反《香港國安法》的執法行動，嚴重侵犯中國內政及司法主權，暴露他們支持反中亂港分子利用選舉危害國家安全的險惡用心。<br />\n<br />\n港澳辦點名批評美國國務卿蓬佩奧上演「最後的瘋狂」，將意圖顛覆國家政權的行徑說成追求民主，強調任何針對中國進行「顔色革命」的圖謀，都注定徹底失敗，並將付出沉重代價。"},{"pid":"96bce80449b81b3310bec68d247838fe836331fe","tid":2362572,"uid":55006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T13:57:26.000Z","msg":"斷交啦"},{"pid":"996dbb5aab586561bc9e7d20c15de65730edeabf","tid":2362572,"uid":18477,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T13:59:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aSsaJO5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaSsaJO5.jpg&h=773c9d62&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n肯開波未呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/vampire_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"063aeba3ac1b4cac3317a40d89fa7e4e4d41d841","tid":2362572,"uid":74171,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"996dbb5aab586561bc9e7d20c15de65730edeabf","tid":2362572,"uid":18477,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T13:59:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aSsaJO5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaSsaJO5.jpg&h=773c9d62&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n肯開波未呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/vampire_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T14:05:27.000Z","msg":"開波，個個都有精銳武器架<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"h